an musicians of Mexican descent]]\n[[Category:American television personalities of Mexican descent]]\n[[Category:Spanish-language singers of the United States]]\n[[Category:Swing singers]]\n[[Category:Traditional pop music singers]]\n[[Category:1919 births]]\n[[Category:1992 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from Boyle Heights, Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:Singers from Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:American radio comedy]]\n[[Category:Capitol Records artists]]\n[[Category:Chicano]]\n[[Category:Golden Age of Mexican cinema]]\n[[Category:Hispanic and Latino American people]]\n[[Category:Mexican-American culture]]\n[[Category:RCA Victor artists]]\n[[Category:American Roman Catholics]]\n[[Category:20th-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:20th-century American singers]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:People from Sun City, Arizona]]\n[[Category:Catholics from Arizona]]\n[[Category:20th-century male singers]]\n[[Category:Male jazz musicians]]\n[[Category:Hispanic and Latino American musicians]]\n", "name_user": "Jonesey95", "label": "safe", "comment": "FixLintererrors", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andy_Russell_(singer)"}
